@startuml
actor User
participant "Browser" as Browser
participant "Django Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Django Backend" as Backend
participant "Azure Face API" as FaceAPI
database "Database" as DB

== User Interaction ==
User -> Browser: Access Face-Find Application
Browser -> Frontend: Request Home Page

== Frontend Control Flow ==
Frontend -> Browser: Render Home Page
Browser -> User: Display Home Page

== Backend Control Flow ==
User -> Browser: Submit Missing Person Report
Browser -> Frontend: Send Report Data
Frontend -> Backend: Forward Report Data
Backend -> DB: Store Report Data
Backend -> FaceAPI: Send Face Image for ID
FaceAPI -> Backend: Return Face ID

Backend -> DB: Store Face ID with Report
Backend -> Frontend: Acknowledge Report Submission
Frontend -> Browser: Confirm Submission
Browser -> User: Show Confirmation

== Face Recognition Flow ==
Backend -> DB: Query for Missing Persons
DB -> Backend: Return Missing Persons Data
Backend -> FaceAPI: Query for Matches with Face IDs
FaceAPI -> Backend: Return Potential Matches

Backend -> DB: Record Potential Matches
Backend -> Frontend: Notify of Matches
Frontend -> User: Email Notification of Matches

@enduml